WEBVTT

00:00,000 --> 00:04,950
Most teams blame tools for weak civic results, but execution discipline is the real gap.

00:05,000 --> 00:09,950
Volume increases quickly, but engagement quality improves only with explicit review loops. Gamification holds up only...

00:10,000 --> 00:14,950
Assign one owner, track one metric, and review one live decision every week.

00:15,000 --> 00:19,950
Run a one-week pilot, capture evidence from real behavior, then adjust immediately.

00:20,000 --> 00:24,950
This usually improves first-pass quality, cleaner engagement handoffs, and faster team adoption.

00:25,000 --> 00:29,950
What is the first review loop you can install this week?
